social_posts.post_text: All I want for Christmas is another day like today!!!! #longbeachny
Awesome holiday gifts!! Quick and easy shopping with super helpful staff! Let us make your shopping experience a pleasure. #happyholidays

unbelievably stoked for @_balaram . We have been blessed to watch him grow up in the shop and become and incredible surfer and even better human. So F-ing stoked that we can say Balaram Stack Is a Pipe Masters Champion. Let’s Go NY!!! Photo @andyryanphotographer

Holiday hours 10am-8:30pm Wednesday, Thursday and Friday. Saturday Christmas Eve 9am til 6:30pm. Thank you again for always being the best customers in the world. We’ve made so many great friends for the past 25 years!! All because of your support!! Thank you again!! Happy Hanukkah and Merry Christmas.

Happy New Year to All.. Hard to believe that we are entering our 25th year in business!!! I think we have seen it all - the surf Biz boom- the Quik pro - Hurricane Sandy - a Pandemic -a couple economic downtowns and more. But the craziest thing we have seen is all the original shop groms grow up, start family’s and bring their kids into the shop. Pretty Nuts. We want to thank all our awesome customers and friends for the continued support. With all of that said we have a few big events planned for this year so stay tuned….

Stoked to announce a much deserved celebration for @_balaram and his recent win at the worlds most prestigious surfing event the Pipeline Masters. Next Friday we will be hosting a signing at the shop from 4-6pm - then it’s off to @brighteyebeer from 7-11 for the “Pipe Master Win” party. Thank you to all the sponsors who helped us organize the event.. @whalebonemagazine @chilli_surfboards_usa @electric @volcomsurf @allegriahotel @brighteyebeer @william.grand

What’s it feel like to be a Pipe Masters Champion!?!? Most of us will never know but stop on by @unsound_surf Tomorrow and ask @_balaram for yourself. The Champ will be in the house from 4-6 tomorrow, we have some posters for the kids, raffles from @electric @volcom and @chilli_surfboards ( if you never had a Chilli you don’t know what your missing - these boards are insane) See you all tomorrow….

Enough is enough. We have been surfing all year round for over 25 years and none of us have ever seen this many dead whales washing up!!! #stopkillingthewhales

Ok here we go, got a once in a NY Lifetime item up for sale - A Signed Kellly Slater Quiksilver Pro New York Jersey framed along side an official event poster ( also signed by the #Goat ) We were gifted this after the Quik Pro, by some of the staffers at Quiksilver for our help with the event. We will be letting this baby go as a fundraising effort for our friends over at the Tommy Brull Foundation ( @tommybrull_foundation ) The TBF is a Long Island based 501(c) charity dedicated to improving the quality of life for people with physical, intellectual and emotional disabilities. This is an incredible piece and would be a great addition to the living room, office or “man cave” .  If interested please DM us with your best offer. ( please serious offers only )

Since we have been slinging surf wax for a quarter of a century, we figured this year would be a great one to stroll down memory lane. So we will be throwing up some of our favorite memories from over the years . The best place to start this stroll? The #unsoundpro We would like to thank the surfers and event sponsors for all the support over the years... Have hundreds of photos / moments we could share. But we need to stick to the insta limit of 10..

@joeyrafe 2023 unsOund Pro winner!! So awesome to see Joe win, we have known Joe since he was around 9 or 10 years old. So it was pretty sick to see how stoked he was to get this win!!❤️ All the other surfers absolutely killed it and made the event exciting to watch from the first heat! All the locals that came to watch-thank you! And special thank you to @longbeach11561 we are all so lucky to have such a beautiful beach to share and let’s keep it that way forever!! (SAY NO TO THE WINDFARM PROJECT-come sign the petition at the shop) Extra special thank you to Chris from @surfesany for running an extra smooth stress free event! Thank you to everyone who helped out especially the judges and @unclericoswax @__dkat__ for being a sponsor! Until next year and thank you again to everyone! All photos by @fullnelson_photo
